\text{content = 
<div id="conteneur">
  <canvas id="dessin" width="400" height="250" style="cursor: default;"></canvas>

  <div class="bloc">
    <input type="checkbox" id="bangles" checked="">
    <label for="bangles" id="langles">Angles</label>
  </div>
  <div class="bloc">
	<input type="checkbox" id="breflechi" checked="">
    <label for="breflechi" id="lreflechi">Rayon réfléchi</label>
  </div>
  <div class="bloc">
	<input type="checkbox" id="brefracte" checked="">
    <label for="brefracte" id="lrefracte">Rayon réfracté</label>
  </div>
</div>}

\text{abs=}
\for{j=1 to 9}{
\text{abs=\abs
text black,12+40*\j,408,small,0.\j}
}

\text{ord=}
\for{i=1 to 9}{
\text{ord=\ord
text black,1,400-40*\i,small,0.\i}
}

\text{dessin=draw(420,420
parallel 0,0,0,420,20,0,21,grey
parallel 0,0,420,0,0,20,21,grey
arrow 20,420,20,0,10,black
arrow 0,400,420,400,10,black
parallel 60,392,60,408,40,0,9,black
parallel 12,360,32,360,0,-40,9,black
text blue,370, 380,medium,sin(i2)
text red,30, 15,medium,sin(i1)
text black,10,407,small,0
\abs
\ord
)
}
\statement{

  \content
  <script src="\imagedir/refraction.js"></script>
<script>
n1 = \n1; n2 = \n2;
window.addEventListener("load", adapterTaille,  passiveSupported ? { passive: false } : false);
</script>
<br/>
On considčre le milieu 1 (en blanc sur l'animation ci-dessus) d'indice n<sub>1</sub>=
\n1. On souhaite déterminer l'indice n<sub>2</sub> du milieu 2 (en bleu sur l'animation 
ci-dessus).
<div class="wims_instruction"> Les angles seront donnés ŕ l'unité prčs et les sinus seront donnés avec <span class="wims_emph">
3 chiffres significatifs.</span></div>
<div class="wims_question">
1. A l'aide de l'animation précédente, compléter le tableau ci-dessous:

<table class="wimscenter wimsborder">
<tr><th>Angle d'incidence (<span class="i1">i<sub>1</sub></span>)</th><th>0</th><th>\i11</th><th>\i12</th><th>\i13</th><th>\i14</th></tr>
<tr><th>Angle de réfraction (<span class="i2">i<sub>2</sub></span>)</th><td>\embed{r1,10}</th><th>\embed{r2,10}</td><td>\embed{r3,10}</td><td>\embed{r4,10}</td><td>\embed{r5,10}</td></tr>
<tr><th><span class="i2">sin(i<sub>2</sub>)</span></th><td>\embed{r6,10}</td><td>\embed{r7,10}</td><td>\embed{r8,10}</td><td>\embed{r9,10}</td><td>\embed{r10,10}</td></tr>
<tr><th><span class="i1">sin(i<sub>1</sub>)</span></th><td>\embed{r11,10}</td><td>\embed{r12,10}</td><td>\embed{r13,10}</td><td>\embed{r14,10}</td><td>\embed{r15,10}</td></tr>

</table>

<div class="spacer">2. Placer ensuite les points dans le repčre suivant (on fera attention ŕ l'abscisse et ŕ l'ordonnée):
<div class="center"> \embed{r16,420x420}</div></div>

3. Compléter les phrases suivantes:
<div class="spacer">Les grandeurs <span class="i2">sin(i<sub>2</sub>)</span> et <span class="i1">sin(i<sub>1</sub>)</span>
sont \embed{r17,10}. La courbe obtenue est caractéristique d'une fonction \embed{r18,10}.</div>
<div>
4. Le coefficient directeur est égal ŕ l'indice n<sub>2</sub> recherché. A l'aide de votre graphique, calculer la valeur de
n<sub>2</sub>=\embed{r19,10}.</div>
<div>
5. En déduire la vitesse de propagation de la lumičre dans le milieu 2: v=\embed{r20,10}.
<script>creelaser("\imagedir/laser.png");</script></div></div>
<div class="wims_instruction">
Ne pas oublier d'indiquer l'unité.</div>
}.
\answer{}{0}{type=numeric}{weight=2}
\answer{}{\i21}{type=numeric}{weight=2}
\answer{}{\i22}{type=numeric}{weight=2}
\answer{}{\i23}{type=numeric}{weight=2}
\answer{}{\i24}{type=numeric}{weight=2}

\answer{}{0}{type=numeric}{weight=2}
\answer{}{\sini21}{type=numeric}{weight=1}
\answer{}{\sini22}{type=numeric}{weight=1}
\answer{}{\sini23}{type=numeric}{weight=1}
\answer{}{\sini24}{type=numeric}{weight=1}

\answer{}{0}{type=numeric}{weight=2}
\answer{}{\sini11}{type=numeric}{weight=1}
\answer{}{\sini12}{type=numeric}{weight=1}
\answer{}{\sini13}{type=numeric}{weight=1}
\answer{}{\sini14}{type=numeric}{weight=1}



\answer{}{\dessin;points,20,400,20+\sini21*400,400-\sini11*400,20+\sini22*400,400-\sini12*400,20+\sini23*400,
400-\sini13*400,20+\sini24*400,400-\sini14*400}{type=jsxgraphcurve}{weight=4}

\answer{}{proportionnelles}{type=atext}{weight=1}
\answer{}{linéaire}{type=atext}{weight=1}
\answer{n2=}{\n2}{type=numeric}{weight=4}
\answer{v=}{\v km/s}{type=units}{weight=2}
